  <h1>Guides</h1>
  <p>Plain-language guides covering the major topics. Each is written and reviewed by our editorial team.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/how-ada-damages-are-calculated">How ADA Damages Are Calculated</a></h3>
  <p>Detailed walkthrough of back pay, front pay, compensatory and punitive damages, employer-size caps, and attorney fees under ADA Title I.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/types-of-ada-violations">Types of ADA Violations</a></h3>
  <p>Overview of Title I, II, and III violations, the reasonable accommodation framework, and perceived disability claims.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/what-to-do-after-ada-violation">What to Do After an ADA Violation</a></h3>
  <p>Step-by-step guidance: documenting the violation, the EEOC process, filing deadlines, and finding counsel.</p>
  <h3><a href="/guides/common-ada-claim-misconceptions">Common ADA Claim Misconceptions</a></h3>
  <p>Twelve common misunderstandings about ADA claims, filing requirements, disability definitions, and damages.</p>
  <ul style="margin-top:2rem">
    <li><a href="/case-types">Case types overview</a></li>
